    "author_association": "NONE",
    "body": "Would it be possible to implement a signcolumn on the right side? Plugins could be build to use it as a scrollbar/minimap or as an indicator for warnings or highlighted search-results. Maybe it should be even possible to use both for indications and scrollbar like in modern guis/ides. Preferably, it should be general enough that it should be not limited to the usecases I mentioned. This also could be used for guis like oni.",
