            "author_association": "NONE",
            "body": "I have another use case for this idea, which is to right align indicators in a tree plugin. I have hacked this in by adding spaces or truncating text, but that requires me to add a polling loop to check for resizes and then re-render the whole buffer on each resize. If I could just use a right hand sign column this would be so much better. I'm sure many other plugins would utilize this feature:\r\n\r\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/5160605/178284611-5ba97415-c44e-49a5-b32e-c25a1979bd71.png)\r\n\r\n",
